name: Caramel
tagline: A bootstrap project to create fully dynamic websites using jaggery
body:
### Lets Start Tasting Caramel
Caramel is a MVC framework built for [Jaggery](http://jaggeryjs.org). The intent of the framework is to bootstrap application development and enforce a standard for developing web applications using Jaggery. By no means Caramel trying to lock down developer creativity or freedom but simply trying enforce discipline to large development teams working on Jaggery projects.
